dct_title_s: Ward, Lock, & Co.'s plan of the city of Paris
dct_alternative_sm: Plan of the city of Paris
dct_description_sm: John Bartholomew & Son, Ltd., Edinr. ; Ward, Lock, & Co., Ltd., Warwick House, Salisbury Square, London.

Shows railways (including underground and under construction), underground stations, tramways, streets, waterways, various locations and points of interest, cemeteries, parks, vegetation and topography of parks.
"The thick lines show squares a mile each way; the thin ones half-mile squares"
